        {
          "text": "User Story:",
          "bold": true
        },
        {
          "text": " As a new AVAnnotate user, I want to learn and understand the features of AVAnnotate so that I can build my own AVAnnotate projects. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Description:",
          "bold": true
        },
        {
          "text": " This Documentation Project is an excellent introduction to AVAnnotate’s features, explaining how and why AVAnnotate can be used. It demonstrates both how projects are constructed (Documentation) and how projects can be effectively presented to an audience (Narrative). "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": ""
