          "bold": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "numbered-list",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "list-item",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Read the Documentation and Narrative sections on each page of the Documentation Project in order to learn about AVAnnotate’s features"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "list-item",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Using your own audio or audiovisual records, annotations, and tags, you can create your own AVAnnotate project using the information gleaned from the Documentation Project "
